---
title: Swedish Meatloaves with Mashed Potatoes, Roasted Carrots, and Currant Jam
description: When you think about it, a meatloaf is just an oversized meatball. So in this recipe, where we’re taking Swedish meatballs and giving them the loaf treatment, things are only gonna be bigger and better than before. These warmly spiced beef meatloaves are smothered in a rich gravy and served with mashed potatoes, roasted carrots, and currant jam to the side—in other words, enough deliciousness to fill out a smorgasbord.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5c670407c445fa5591505a02-2c7ad0c5.jpg
